{"tid":2419391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"預約系統出錯有市民今搶先接種 6旬翁：作為中國人要幫國家試疫苗！","createTime":"2021-02-23T09:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T11:57:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b7caa22219629a014e38d58ff4d7b31f0c1e08a0","tid":2419391,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"國產科興武漢肺炎疫苗今早（23日）凌晨開放予優先群組接受預約，政府今日亦安排200名屬優先群組的人士，到中央圖書館展覽館疫苗接種中心接種國產科興疫苗。預約系統疑有岀錯，今早有部份優先群組市民成功預約即日名額，變相提早接種疫苗。有市民表示，不擔心科興疫苗有副作用，揚言：「中國人梗係支持中國（疫苗）」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/MIZCQEREONC75DCKLJ4R5TPYDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FMIZCQEREONC75DCKLJ4R5TPYDI%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv336wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=19fd46d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FMIZCQEREONC75DCKLJ4R5TPYDI%2F&h=e84fe9ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/MIZCQEREONC75DCKLJ4R5TPYDI/</a>"},{"pid":"2a54d74f91798b63316707e308b8704b9bca90c2","tid":2419391,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔返上去住？"},{"pid":"b2f08d43bcb0370c81f7fe69c63e34b60df28b66","tid":2419391,"uid":18477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"班blue objects好撚鐘意呢種白色底衫㗎喎真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱得滯又可以當面衫嚟用<br />\n物盡其用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577c3137ef50fd85490275989e3f471d352893be","tid":2419391,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T10:04:53.000Z","msg":"應當鼓勵讚揚"},{"pid":"1bae723926a741479164f271490f